flowchart TD
    subgraph Actors
        Actor1[Casual Movie Watcher]
        Actor2[Older User]
    end
    subgraph CreateAccountSystem[Account Creation System]
        CreateAccount((Create Account))
        SetUserPass((Set Username<br/>and Password))
        Email((Add Email))
        Subscriptions((Add Initial<br/>Subscriptions))
        Guide((Account Setup<br/>Guide))
    end

    Actor1 --> CreateAccount
    Actor2 --> CreateAccount
    CreateAccount -->|<<include>>| Guide


    CreateAccount -.->|<<include>>| SetUserPass
    CreateAccount -.->|<<extend>>|Subscriptions
    CreateAccount -.->|<<extend>>|Email